{"tid":1260601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論]國際點睇呢次香港？","createTime":"2019-06-27T01:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T01:49:41.000Z","uid":157470,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fbbdb46ad3b1b8273544a5d070c2e5ace2d12967","tid":1260601,"uid":157470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:25:35.000Z","msg":"點解仲要一次一次考慮國際感受<br />\n我諗佢地會明白二百萬人入面有激進勇武派(好似係)<br />\n而且佢地對示威騷亂嘅武力準備比起香港更多<br />\n我反而認為keep住有活動可以令外國持續關注呢件事<br />\n所以對呢件事有利以冇害<br />\n<br />\nps:中文差講到1999"},{"pid":"c22ed06de17bc15a152a2e3ccb759a63c9823716","tid":1260601,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:26:00.000Z","msg":"1999 , 唔明"},{"pid":"7214a580229d81af5a9b14870750e24bbafc22fb","tid":1260601,"uid":157470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c22ed06de17bc15a152a2e3ccb759a63c9823716","tid":1260601,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:26:00.000Z","msg":"1999 , 唔明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:28:28.000Z","msg":"講下咩唔明<br />\n我試下解釋"},{"pid":"2487e58a744cdde96559bb0a3ccaa9c5fcc067a1","tid":1260601,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:29:31.000Z","msg":"推          <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">大家可以不同意，但記得不譴責！</div></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v91tp44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv91tp44.png&h=ff06b129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">拒絕分化、槍口一致<br />\n對準殺人政權<br />\n不退不讓！</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">堅守底線，<br />\n因我們沒有退讓的理由。</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZK1hpDrSQ9M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZK1hpDrSQ9M&d=7GYMv7TAV12u%2FDK%2BXNcYJUzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=f7f759fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZK1hpDrSQ9M</a><br />\n\t<br />\n未爭取到五項訴求前，<br />\n香港人將「不撤不散」。<br />\n<br />\n五個訴求包括<br />\n1 &bull; 全面撤回送中惡法&amp;nbsp;<br />\n2 &bull; 反對定性暴動&amp;nbsp;<br />\n3 &bull; 釋放抗爭者 撤銷所有控罪&amp;nbsp;<br />\n4 &bull; 追究濫權警察暴行&amp;nbsp;<br />\n5 &bull; 林鄭下台</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/26/232653_dfe28ed01502ee0bc7435027305111eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F26%2F232653_dfe28ed01502ee0bc7435027305111eb.png&h=8cfbbd31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">不撤不退！</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[文宣戰]抗爭告白心聲Poster，</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳！！！！</span> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1259733\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1259733</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可以入post睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好幫手推埋上熱門<br />\n等多啲人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(想share但又懶既直接係最底copy再開！) </span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a6d135afde05bae1eeedab238e128d4132aafe5f","tid":1260601,"uid":134012,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:30:27.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"b651e4493ed92ed7feb9208a73bf6fa9b7bb1c78","tid":1260601,"uid":40652,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:31:38.000Z","msg":"鬼佬覺得你地咁多人得咁少勇武係垃圾<br />\n道德光環持續高企"},{"pid":"0b3a0c814880cbe1d4d09e528e4ce7d0d6cc9175","tid":1260601,"uid":157470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b651e4493ed92ed7feb9208a73bf6fa9b7bb1c78","tid":1260601,"uid"